{"tid":2073651,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國民黨議員張世賢質詢學貓叫春…議場笑翻","createTime":"2020-06-21T13:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T03:35:06.000Z","uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"95b4ee64407f7e7a4c1a7b39e4e8fd1a5d426b8e","tid":2073651,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"台南市議員張世賢今天總質詢時，針對流浪貓狗捕抓問題提出質詢，他並當場學發情期公貓、母貓的淒厲叫聲，聲音超專業，官員聽了忍不住發笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。事後，在議場外的議員蔡旺詮說，他聽到當下，以為議場真的有貓在叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n市長黃偉哲受訪說，「不知道張議員還有這項專長<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3200367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3200367&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=37b067d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3200367&h=f843118a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3200367</a>"},{"pid":"70ae616e64e2741389a990ebf3d50bd64454fed6","tid":2073651,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:11:08.000Z","msg":"張世賢質詢時詢問農業局長謝耀清，台南市1年野貓抓幾隻？他並質疑流浪狗捕捉後閹割再置放回原地（TNVR）的作法擾民，批評應該由愛心人士自己抓回去養。<br />\n<br />\n謝耀清答詢說，置放回原地後會觀察地點是否適合，並要求不要在交通要道、人口密集處飼養。<br />\n<br />\n張世賢隨後詢問市長黃偉哲「公貓母貓看得出來嗎？」他質疑動保處1天野貓恐怕抓不到3隻，「野貓晚上在屋頂跑來跑去，喵喵叫，像鬼打架一樣。」說著說著他當場學起發情期公貓、母貓叫聲，指高吭淒厲的「喵～喵～喵～」是公貓，意思是說「叫你來！」；較輕柔的母貓叫聲則說「不要啦！」<br />\n<br />\n黃偉哲則正經答詢說，「貓比較難抓，公母貓外觀看不出來。」「牠們可能是繁殖期才會這樣叫，可以錄公貓的聲音來引誘捕捉。」不過，列席的官員們則已忍不住在一旁發笑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QXahaDIzXmA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQXahaDIzXmA&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=47f3aefc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QXahaDIzXmA</a>"},{"pid":"e2dbb7ad0754bc798ec273cb979b923b7f0d974e","tid":2073651,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:11:51.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">[&darr;&darr;港獨強心針&darr;&darr;]</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港最強力盟友USA : <br />\n國際反共 形勢大好<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/pAcortX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/pAcortX</a></span></div>"},{"pid":"09b070d7316169e930ce4b0b003e9676a25ecebc","tid":2073651,"uid":42740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:12:47.000Z","msg":"扮得好撚似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27521706ee6eb5a790b6be5a856543ea7222cde7","tid":2073651,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:13:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bkvNeGQbgFI?t=548\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbkvNeGQbgFI%3Ft%3D548&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Y8LrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=001469b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bkvNeGQbgFI?t=548</a>"},{"pid":"12df13ad794295aeb868c2cede0b0bc9e7a24d64","tid":2073651,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:13:42.000Z","msg":"中2病到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75da759092509a1f6c623137957c89e85310aa78","tid":2073651,"uid":276469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/